<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Mohamed Hassan – QA Tester Portfolio</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
:root {
  --bg:      #04050a;
  --surface: #090b12;
  --card:    #0d0f1a;
  --border:  rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --accent:  #e8ff47;
  --accent2: #47ffe8;
  --text:    #eeeef2;
  --muted:   #6b6b80;
  --glow-y:  0 0 50px rgba(232,255,71,0.12);
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:400;line-height:1.7;overflow-x:hidden;cursor:none;}
#cursor{width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);mix-blend-mode:difference;}
#cursor-ring{width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(232,255,71,0.35);border-radius:50%;position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:left 0.15s ease,top 0.15s ease;}
body::after{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='g'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23g)' opacity='0.025'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");pointer-events:none;z-index:998;}

nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:500;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:1.4rem 5rem;background:rgba(4,5,10,0.88);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.nav-logo{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2.5rem;list-style:none;}
.nav-links a{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--accent);}
.nav-cta{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;padding:0.55rem 1.4rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;transition:all 0.2s;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:#f5ff7a;transform:translateY(-1px);}

#hero{min-height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;align-items:center;padding:9rem 5rem 5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;gap:4rem;}
.orb{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(90px);pointer-events:none;}
.orb1{width:500px;height:500px;background:rgba(232,255,71,0.05);top:-80px;right:-80px;}
.orb2{width:400px;height:400px;background:rgba(71,255,232,0.04);bottom:-60px;left:30%;}
.hero-left{position:relative;z-index:2;}
.hero-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--accent);background:rgba(232,255,71,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(232,255,71,0.2);padding:0.45rem 1.1rem;border-radius:3px;margin-bottom:2.2rem;animation:fadeUp 0.9s ease both;}
.hero-tag span{width:5px;height:5px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:blink 1.8s infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:0.15;}}
h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,6vw,5.8rem);line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.8rem;animation:fadeUp 0.9s 0.1s ease both;}
h1 .hi{font-style:italic;font-weight:400;color:var(--accent);}
.hero-desc{font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:420px;margin-bottom:3rem;line-height:1.8;animation:fadeUp 0.9s 0.2s ease both;}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;animation:fadeUp 0.9s 0.3s ease both;}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.9rem 2.2rem;border-radius:5px;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.22s;cursor:none;border:none;}
.btn-p{background:var(--accent);color:#000;}
.btn-p:hover{background:#f5ff7a;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--glow-y);}
.btn-o{background:transparent;color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);}
.btn-o:hover{border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.4);color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.hero-right{position:relative;z-index:2;animation:fadeUp 0.9s 0.35s ease both;}
.hcard{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.hcard::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),transparent);}
.hc-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.hc-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.chip{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;padding:0.35rem 0.9rem;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(232,255,71,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(232,255,71,0.15);color:var(--accent);}
.hc-div{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:1.5rem 0;}
.hc-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1rem;}
.hstat{text-align:center;}
.hstat-n{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--accent);display:block;line-height:1;}
.hstat-l{font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:0.3rem;display:block;}
.hc-avail{margin-top:1.8rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);}
.avail-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#4ade80;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.5);animation:blink 2s infinite;flex-shrink:0;}

.sec{padding:7rem 5rem;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;}
.sec-full{background:var(--surface);padding:7rem 0;}
.sec-full .sec-in{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 5rem;}
.stag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:0.8rem;display:block;}
.stitle{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.sdesc{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.95rem;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:3.5rem;line-height:1.8;}

/* Skills */
.skills-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(290px,1fr));gap:1px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;}
.ski{background:var(--card);padding:2rem;transition:background 0.3s;}
.ski:hover{background:#111320;}
.ski-icon{font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.ski-name{font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;}
.ski-desc{font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;}
.ski-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.4rem;margin-top:1.1rem;}
.ski-chip{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;padding:0.2rem 0.65rem;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(232,255,71,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(232,255,71,0.15);color:var(--accent);}

/* Services */
.svc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(270px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;}
.svc{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:2.2rem;transition:all 0.3s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.svc::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform 0.35s;}
.svc:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.15);box-shadow:var(--glow-y);}
.svc:hover::after{transform:scaleX(1);}
.svc-num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1.4rem;}
.svc-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.35rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;}
.svc-desc{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;}
.svc-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.45rem;margin-top:1.4rem;}
.tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;padding:0.25rem 0.7rem;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(71,255,232,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(71,255,232,0.15);color:var(--accent2);}

/* Projects */
.proj-sec-head{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:3.5rem;}
#projects-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;}
.proj-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s;}
.proj-card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.2);box-shadow:var(--glow-y);}
.proj-img{width:100%;height:185px;object-fit:cover;display:block;}
.proj-img-placeholder{width:100%;height:185px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d0f1a,#111320);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:2.8rem;}
.proj-body{padding:1.6rem;}
.proj-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.proj-desc{font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.proj-footer{display:flex;gap:0.6rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.proj-link{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;padding:0.3rem 0.9rem;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;background:rgba(232,255,71,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(232,255,71,0.2);color:var(--accent);}
.proj-link:hover{background:rgba(232,255,71,0.16);}
.proj-empty{grid-column:1/-1;text-align:center;padding:4rem 2rem;color:var(--muted);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.78rem;border:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;line-height:2;}

/* About */
.usp-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;}
.usp-q{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2rem);line-height:1.45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.usp-q em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);}
.usp-body{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;}
.usp-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;}
.ustat{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.6rem;text-align:center;transition:all 0.3s;}
.ustat:hover{border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.2);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.ustat-n{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--accent);display:block;line-height:1;}
.ustat-l{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:0.4rem;display:block;}

/* Contact */
.contact-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:start;}
.clinks{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;margin-top:2rem;}
.clink{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.3rem 1.6rem;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);transition:all 0.25s;}
.clink:hover{border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.3);color:var(--accent);transform:translateX(8px);box-shadow:var(--glow-y);}
.ci-icon{font-size:1.3rem;width:36px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.ci-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);display:block;margin-bottom:0.2rem;}
.ci-val{font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;}
.cform{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;}
.finput{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem 1.3rem;color:var(--text);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;outline:none;width:100%;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
.finput::placeholder{color:var(--muted);}
.finput:focus{border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.4);}
textarea.finput{resize:vertical;min-height:130px;}

footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:2rem 5rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.fcopy{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--muted);}
.fdot{color:var(--accent);}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);transition:opacity 0.75s ease,transform 0.75s ease;}
.reveal.on{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

/* ======= ADMIN ======= */
#admin-page{display:none;min-height:100vh;background:var(--bg);padding:8rem 5rem 5rem;}
#admin-page.active{display:block;}
#main-page.hidden{display:none;}
.admin-header{margin-bottom:3rem;}
.admin-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2rem;}
.admin-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start;}
.admin-form-wrap{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.admin-form-wrap::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),transparent);}
.admin-form-title{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:1.8rem;}
.admin-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.1rem;}
.flabel{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;}
.fgroup{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.file-upload{background:var(--surface);border:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:8px;padding:1.4rem;text-align:center;transition:all 0.2s;position:relative;cursor:pointer;}
.file-upload:hover{border-color:rgba(232,255,71,0.3);}
.file-upload input[type="file"]{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;cursor:pointer;width:100%;height:100%;}
.file-upload-icon{font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;}
.file-upload-text{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--muted);}
.file-name-ok{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--accent);margin-top:0.5rem;word-break:break-all;}
.admin-list-title{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:1rem;}
.admin-projects-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.85rem;}
.admin-proj-item{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.1rem 1.4rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;}
.admin-proj-thumb{width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:#111320;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;}
.admin-proj-thumb img{width:50px;height:50px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;}
.admin-proj-info{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.admin-proj-name{font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.admin-proj-subdesc{font-size:0.73rem;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.admin-proj-del{background:rgba(255,80,80,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,80,80,0.18);color:#ff6060;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:4px;cursor:none;transition:all 0.2s;flex-shrink:0;}
.admin-proj-del:hover{background:rgba(255,80,80,0.2);}
.admin-empty{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2rem;border:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:8px;}
.form-msg{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;text-align:center;min-height:1.2rem;}

@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:1.1rem 1.8rem;}
  .nav-links,.nav-cta{display:none;}
  #hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:8rem 1.8rem 4rem;gap:2rem;}
  .hero-right{display:none;}
  .sec{padding:5rem 1.8rem;}
  .sec-full .sec-in{padding:0 1.8rem;}
  .usp-wrap,.contact-wrap,.admin-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  footer{flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;}
  #admin-page{padding:7rem 1.8rem 4rem;}
  .proj-sec-head{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="cursor"></div>
<div id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- ========== MAIN PAGE ========== -->
<div id="main-page">

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">MH <span style="color:var(--muted)">//</span> QA Tester</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Hire Me</a>
</nav>

<div id="hero">
  <div class="orb orb1"></div>
  <div class="orb orb2"></div>
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-tag"><span></span> Available for Freelance Work</div>
    <h1>Mohamed<br/><span class="hi">Hassan</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">QA Tester specializing in manual testing, API testing, bug reporting, and delivering high-quality web experiences — fast and with precision.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-p">Get In Touch →</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-o">View Services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hcard">
      <div class="hc-lbl">// Core Skills</div>
      <div class="hc-chips">
        <span class="chip">Manual Testing</span>
        <span class="chip">API Testing</span>
        <span class="chip">Bug Reporting</span>
        <span class="chip">UI/UX Testing</span>
        <span class="chip">DevTools</span>
        <span class="chip">Cross-Browser</span>
        <span class="chip">Jira / Trello</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hc-div"></div>
      <div class="hc-stats">
        <div class="hstat"><span class="hstat-n">1–2</span><span class="hstat-l">Day Delivery</span></div>
        <div class="hstat"><span class="hstat-n">5</span><span class="hstat-l">Services</span></div>
        <div class="hstat"><span class="hstat-n">$25</span><span class="hstat-l">Starting</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hc-avail">
        <div class="avail-dot"></div>
        Open to new projects right now
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<div id="skills" class="sec-full">
  <div class="sec-in">
    <span class="stag reveal">What I Know</span>
    <h2 class="stitle reveal">Skills & Tools</h2>
    <p class="sdesc reveal">Every bug tells a story. I use the right tools to find, document, and communicate them clearly.</p>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="ski reveal">
        <div class="ski-icon">🔍</div>
        <div class="ski-name">Manual Testing</div>
        <div class="ski-desc">Thorough functional and exploratory testing to catch issues before they reach users.</div>
        <div class="ski-chips"><span class="ski-chip">Functional</span><span class="ski-chip">Exploratory</span><span class="ski-chip">Smoke</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ski reveal">
        <div class="ski-icon">🎨</div>
        <div class="ski-name">UI/UX Testing</div>
        <div class="ski-desc">Evaluating layout, navigation, responsiveness, and overall user experience quality.</div>
        <div class="ski-chips"><span class="ski-chip">Responsive</span><span class="ski-chip">Accessibility</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ski reveal">
        <div class="ski-icon">🐛</div>
        <div class="ski-name">Bug Reporting</div>
        <div class="ski-desc">Clear, structured bug reports with steps to reproduce, screenshots, and severity levels.</div>
        <div class="ski-chips"><span class="ski-chip">Steps to Repro</span><span class="ski-chip">Severity</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ski reveal">
        <div class="ski-icon">🌐</div>
        <div class="ski-name">Cross-Browser Testing</div>
        <div class="ski-desc">Testing on Chrome, Firefox, Edge, and Safari to ensure consistent behavior across all browsers.</div>
        <div class="ski-chips"><span class="ski-chip">Chrome</span><span class="ski-chip">Firefox</span><span class="ski-chip">Edge</span><span class="ski-chip">Safari</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ski reveal">
        <div class="ski-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="ski-name">API Testing</div>
        <div class="ski-desc">Testing REST APIs using Postman — validating endpoints, status codes, request/response structure, and error handling.</div>
        <div class="ski-chips"><span class="ski-chip">Postman</span><span class="ski-chip">REST</span><span class="ski-chip">JSON</span><span class="ski-chip">Status Codes</span></div>
